      <title>日本首相澄清丑闻的努力未能提高民意调查支持率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/japan-pm-s-bid-to-clear-scandal-fails-to-improve-poll-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄试图通过惩罚执政党议员来扭转资金丑闻，几天后他的内阁支持率跌至上任以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/japan-pm-s-bid-to-clear-scandal-fails-to-improve-poll-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 01:37:49 GMT</pubDate>
